snippet.title: Amber Heard must hand over arrest record in Depp defamation case
snippet.description:
Judge Bruce White denied some of the requests for documents by Depp’s legal team but ordered Amber Heard to produce her arrest records. 
#JusticeForJohnnyDepp #JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard
